title: Feature spike predownloading
body:
This tries to solve the problem of the breaking on build process.
The thing was that when we use 'speechbrain/spkrec-ecapa-voxceleb', SpeechBrain treied to download the model from HugginFace and break the build. To solve this, we can download the model and use it on the project.
Observation: bacause of the predownloading, the file pretrained_models is a bit too large almost forcing Git LFS.

Fixes #68
